# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` for local `wrangler dev`. Do NOT commit `.dev.vars`.
#
# AUTH_TOKEN: a long, hard-to-guess random string. It becomes part of your MCP URL:
#   https://<worker>.workers.dev/<AUTH_TOKEN>/mcp   (Streamable HTTP)
#   https://<worker>.workers.dev/<AUTH_TOKEN>/sse    (SSE)
# Generate one (PowerShell): [Convert]::ToBase64String((1..32 | % {Get-Random -Max 256})) -replace '[+/=]','x'
AUTH_TOKEN='replace-with-a-long-random-string'
